2022-04-06
  Linuxon lock timeout tamogatas
    fsetlock: varakozas nelkul lockol
    fwaitlock: korlatlan varkozassal lockol
    ftimeoutlock: CCCLK_TIMEOUT ideig varva a lockol
  Mikor, mivel lockol
    fopen protokoll lock : ftimeoutlock
    btbtx page lock      : fwaitlock
    btbtx record lock    : ftimeoutlock
  Ha CCCLK_TIMEOUT<=0, akkor ftimeoutlock=fsetlock;
  Linuxon alarm() fuggveny + SIGALRM kezelese tamogatva;
  Ha egy programban lockolas van, es CCCLK_TIMEOUT>0,
  akkor a lock mechanizmus atveszi a SIGALRM kezelest;

2022-03-28
   elirasok javitva;

2022-03-28
   tabobj: __bt_read()-ben es __bt_read1()-ben shared pagelock;

2022-03-27
  Linux/Windows kozos lock interfesz: flock.cpp-ben _ccc_lock() es _ccc_unlock();
  fsetlock/fwaitlock/funlock atirva _ccc_lock()/_ccc_unlock()-ra;
  filecreat.cpp-ben a fileshare protokol lock atirva _ccc_lock()-ra;
  tabobj: _writechangelog_mutex atirva fwaitlock-ra (cpp->prg);
  tabobj: __bt_pagelock() atirva _ccc_lock()/_ccc_unlock()-ra;
  protokoll lock offsetek (valtozott a helyuk):
    filelock : low=0        high=LK_OFFSET_FILE     (253)
    pagelock : low=2*pgno   high=LK_OFFSET_PAGE     (254)
    reclock  : low=recpos   high=LK_OFFSET_RECORD   (255)
  tabobj: mpool.cpp-ben a lapolvasas tobbszor probalva;
  Windowson is bekapcsolva a 64 bit fileoffset tamogatas;

2022-03-26 CCC3-Windows stat javitas:
  Win1709-en nem lehet (struct *_stat)-ot (struct *stat)-ra castolni.
  (Korabban lehetett, ujabb Windowsokon most is lehet.)   Javitva stat(),
  stat_st_mode(), stat_st_size(). Csak a CCC3-Windows ag erintett.

2022-03-25 lock fuggvenyek fsetlock/fwaitlock
  varakozas nelkul lockol:
    fsetlock(fd, offset, length, exclusive/shared)
    fsetlock(fd, lowoffs, highoffs, exclusive/shared)
  varakozassal lockol:
    fwaitlock(fd, offset, length, exclusive/shared)
    fwaitlock(fd, lowoffs, highoffs, exclusive/shared)
  ugyanaz a parameterezes, az utolso logikai parameter defaultja .t. (exclusive);

2022-03-25 ppo2cpp 5.4.1:
  A kodgenerator strtoul helyett strtoull-lel konvertalja a hexa szamokat.
  (Windowson a C++ kodba csonkitva irodtak ki a 32 bitnel nagyobb hexa szamok.)
  Windowson a mingw forditasi opcioiba bekerult a -DFILE_OFFSET_BITS=64.
  (Ezzel Windowson is sizeof(off_t)==8, Linuxon ez korabban is igy volt.)


